job_responsibilities=Marketing Manager – Key Responsibilities

1) Develop, implement, and manage comprehensive marketing strategies to build brand awareness and drive growth.
2) Plan and oversee campaigns across digital, social, email, and offline channels to ensure consistency and impact.
3) Collaborate with cross-functional teams (sales, product, design, etc.) to align marketing strategies with business goals.
4) Manage and optimize the company’s online presence, including website content, SEO, and social media.
5) Track, measure, and report on the performance of marketing campaigns against KPIs and ROI.
6) Lead, mentor, and develop the marketing team to achieve department objectives.
7) Build and maintain strong relationships with external partners, media agencies, and vendors.
8) Manage the marketing budget effectively to maximize impact and efficiency.